  <h1>Ministry Today proudly presents <em>Greenelines</em>, a new blog from Dr. Steve Greene.</h1>
  <p>Dr. Greene writes on a wide range of topics important to leaders, church administrators and young leaders in development.</p>
  <p>He has lead business organizations, served as a dean of a college of business and lead as a senior pastor. Greene's primary focus is to equip the leaders of saints.</p>
