						<h1><a href="/ministry-outreach/evangelism/21532-evangelism-never-changes-but-the-methods-do">Evangelism Never Changes, but the Methods Do</a></h1>
			<div class="contentBody"><p>While we should be thankful the message of evangelism never changes, we should pray that we will always be sensitive to the changing methods so that many people will have the opportunity to hear the good news of Jesus Christ.</p></div>
